      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2019-06-20</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-03-04T14:14:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Lady Liberty Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill sets a floor of 110,000 for the maximum number of refugees who may be admitted into the United States each fiscal year. Under current law, the President sets the annual cap on refugee admissions at the beginning of each fiscal year. (The cap for FY2020 is 18,000, and the cap for FY2019 was 30,000.)</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Lady Liberty Act of 2019</title>
